snippet.title: Yoshi's Fabrication Station - Flutterfest Contest Spotlight
snippet.description:
These are the top 3 entries of the Flutterfest contest of YFS!

Footage by Vortoxium
Editing & thumbnail by MrGerund
Refer to the video and/or timestamps for the level creators

Timestamps
0:00 Intro
0:07 Mount Helium by Pierre (3)
2:28 Angel Falls by AllenCaspe9510 (2)
7:46 The Moonlit Flutter Ship by Kelux93 (1)

Play the most recent version of YFS here:
https://luigibonus.com/games/yoshisfabricationstation/

Don't miss any updates & share your levels by joining our discord!
https://discord.gg/5vNPQ2BQYP

Yoshi's Fabrication Station is a Yoshi's Island fangame you can freely play in your browser, execute as a browser app or download on your PC. You can create your own levels and share them on our official site:
https://levelsharesquare.com/
